<li> <a href="0053.html"><b>Homosexuality in the SDA church</b></a> <a name="53"><i>Bill and TracyAnne Nickless</i></a>
<li> <a href="0054.html"><b>Re: Genetic damage; spiritual things</b></a> <a name="54"><i>Fred Christiansen</i></a>
