View Magazine is a new magazine designed for Seventh-day Adventists ages<br>
20-30, featuring articles and features by us and about us.  It will be a<br>
monthly, in the format of an 8-page broadside on newsprint, printed in<br>
2-color.  Subscriptions are available from the Review + Herald (address<br>
on request).<br>
 <br>
As a member of a focus group, I was able to review the preview issue of<br>
this magazine, and found it quite interesting.<br>
 <br>
Steve Timm<br>
