<title>Jul_1992: Re: Special day of prayer</title>
<h1>Re: Special day of prayer</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Tue,  7 Jul 1992 22:30:38 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#23">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#23">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#23">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#23">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0024.html">Danny Kumamoto: "accepting creationism?"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0022.html">Steven Timm: "Re: "Discovered--Noah's Ark""</a>
<li> <b>Maybe in reply to:</b> <a href="0015.html">Steven Timm: "Special day of prayer"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
