This isn't specifically on creationism but it is on "science".  I was<br>
recently reading some of Karl Popper's writings on the philosophy of<br>
science.  He said something very interesting.  It went something like<br>
this:<br>
<p>
	Science, like religion, is based on faith but is a little<br>
	less honest about its need to do so.<br>
<p>
Cheryl<br>
