In regard to the church and state, did anyone notice the latest Review<br>
where it talks about Lynwood Adventist Academy in California?<br>
It appears that the public school district has won its long struggle<br>
to take over the property of the school by eminent domain.  The compensation<br>
for this was more than the district was originally going to pay, but less<br>
than what the church had asked for.  Scary if you ask me.<br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
