I've noticed a few cases lately where people insert ^L (control-L) at<br>
the top of messages.  This messes up mail systems.  I use a very<br>
common UNIX mail system (MH Mail) and it clears my screen while in the<br>
middle of displaying a list of message summaries.<br>
