     __________             
    / ________() 
   / /\______      "If God is for us, who can be against us?"         Lisa Parry
  / /_/_____()     --Romans 8:31, last sentence                parry@andrews.edu
 /_________  
 L________()  
</pre>
<!-- body="end" -->
<p>
<ul>
