<title>Jul_1992: homosexuality and genes</title>
<h1>homosexuality and genes</h1>
McCluskey G (<i>glenm@usl.com</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 22 Jul 92 14:44:09 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#58">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#58">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#58">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#58">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0059.html">Joanne Figueiredo: "Correction"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0057.html">Paul Gates: "Re: Homosexuality in the SDA church"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
