<title>Jul_1992: thanx/ dating/ marriage</title>
<h1>thanx/ dating/ marriage</h1>
Alice Fay Martin (<i>armg9488@uxa.cso.uiuc.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 30 Jul 1992 11:43:02 -0500</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#73">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#73">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#73">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#73">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0074.html">Dan Blake: "Marriage outside the faith"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0072.html">Steven Timm: "Sexual Ethics in the Adventist Ministry"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
