<title>Jun_1992: Pathfinders</title>
<h1>Pathfinders</h1>
Lola (<i>AAGAARD%morekypr.BITNET@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 02 Jun 92 11:01:00 EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#5">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#5">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#5">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#5">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0006.html">Dave Buxton: "HIGH SABBATH - The Jews Answer"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0004.html">Scott Mattes: "Passing something along to you"</a>
