<h1>Re: Anger and how to deal with it</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Fri,  5 Jun 1992 01:33:15 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#14">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#14">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#14">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#14">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0015.html">Steven Timm: "I'm Going To Switzerland For Two Weeks"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0013.html">Cheryl Berthelsen: "Anger and how to deal with it"</a>
