Friends, co-listers, brothers, sisters, jews and gentiles :-)<br>
 <br>
This is the last message I am sending to both lists from<br>
UIC.<br>
 <br>
I have recently graduated with a B.A. in Political Science and<br>
Sociology.  In about two weeks, my account will be cancelled.<br>
 <br>
I have enjoyed being a member of both lists for the past 18<br>
months.  I only wish the traffic in SDa-L will one day increase.<br>
 <br>
Since I have enjoyed the lists so much, I decided to apply<br>
for graduate school so that my computer access would not end :-)<br>
 <br>
So I did.  Next fall, I will start graduate studies at the<br>
University of Chicago (in political science).  At that time,<br>
as soon as I get a computer accout, I will subscribe again<br>
to both lists.<br>
 <br>
In the meantime, I wish everyone a happy summer and as someone<br>
says,<br>
 <br>
hasta la vista, baby!!!   (instead of baby, read, friends, please).<br>
 <br>
Patricio Navia.<br>
 <br>
(scott, could you please disconnect me from sdanet?, I am<br>
taking my name out of sda-l directly  from the loma linda listserv).<br>
