Dear SDA-L<br>
 <br>
Well, after some heroics by the LLUVM system people and lots of hassles<br>
for Enoch, I am now a full owner of SDA-L and ready to help with various<br>
requests that have been piling up during our technical difficulties.<br>
 <br>
Some changes that have already been made:<br>
Everyone's distribution policy has been set to RENEW so that if you<br>
move away on us or something the LISTSERV will ask you to confirm your<br>
subscription automatically.<br>
 <br>
Also, we have SET NOMAIL those people whose addresses have been bouncing<br>
back with undeliverable mail.  So now it is possible to make traffic on<br>
SDA-L without drowning its owners in error messages.<br>
 <br>
Again, please address any problems with unanswered list requests to me<br>
at st0o@andrew.cmu.edu or st0o@ANDREW.Bitnet<br>
 <br>
Steve Timm<br>
