last day I <br>
was there, advertising an ecumenical conference on the Bible, which<br>
seemed to be cooperative between most of the denominations including<br>
Evangelical, Catholic, and Adventist.  This seems an unusual instance of<br>
cooperation.<br>
Any clues what may be going on here?<br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
