<h1>Re: Is abortion sin? (fwd)</h1>
Woody Baker (<i>woody@knapper.cactus.org</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 12 Aug 1994 08:58:57 -0500</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#2">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#2">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#2">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#2">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0003.html">Bill Sands Jr.: "The Abortion Solution..."</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0001.html">Woody Baker: "Re: #2 response to Internet Replies/ASDAL"</a>
