George,<br>
<p>
How lucky you are!  Your wife didn't have an abortion in any sense<br>
of the word, which is why you have two LIVING children.  Were we<br>
to know what besetting sins you and your wife fight against every<br>
day, might we conclude that your two children were better off<br>
killed before birth so they don't grow up to commit the same sins<br>
as you?  <br>
<p>
I'm puzzled as to why it's so easy for people to speak of death as<br>
a better "option" than life, when only the living can express<br>
their opinions on the matter, never the dead babies who have been<br>
denied the opportunity to experience life for themselves?<br>
<p>
Joseph Miceli <br>
<!-- body="end" -->
