<title>Aug2_1994: Re: Is abortion sin?</title>
<h1>Re: Is abortion sin?</h1>
Joseph Miceli (<i>slick@reason.win.net</i>)<br>
<i>Sat, 13 Aug 1994 12:03:04</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#15">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#15">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#15">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#15">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0016.html">Joseph Miceli: "Re: 1844 a mistake?"</a>
