after the "fall", I wonder if God created skunks in Eden. And<br>
if there were skunks in Eden, why were they equipped with such<br>
a stink...<br>
<p>
Just wondering...were there skunks in Eden?<br>
<p>
Bill Sands, Jr.<br>
