<title>Aug2_1994: Auditing SDA Education...</title>
<h1>Auditing SDA Education...</h1>
Bill Sands Jr. (<i>sands@andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Sun, 14 Aug 1994 18:26:44 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
