<title>Aug2_1994: Re: Punishment vs consequences</title>
<h1>Re: Punishment vs consequences</h1>
Joseph Miceli (<i>miceli@reason.win.net</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 15 Aug 1994 21:22:32</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#70">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#70">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#70">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#70">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
