Theo "Ted" Barker wrote:<br>
<p>
<i>&gt; What would the Operation Rescue activists do if someone were to attend one</i><br>
<i>&gt; of their protests and start saying "PREVENT abortions!" quietly and hand</i><br>
<i>&gt; out condoms and spermacide to everyone in sight?</i><br>
<p>
That would be like holding seminars on "safe bank robbery", methinks!  The<br>
point is, no sin is "safe", perhaps because God designed things that way.<br>
While what you're hypothesizing would be slightly preferable to abortion, I<br>
suppose, it's not the BEST solution.<br>
<p>
I don't know what "Operation Rescue" would do.  What do you suppose YOUR<br>
pastor would do if someone tried that in the middle of one of the services<br>
at YOUR church?<br>
