<h1>Re: "absent from the body... home with the Lord"</h1>
Dan Crowe (<i>dcrowe@puc.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 17 Aug 1994 15:27:11 -0700 (PDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#102">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#102">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#102">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#102">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0103.html">Harry Salvini: "Re: 1844  (*^&amp;$%^$&amp;$^)"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0101.html">Dan Drazen: "Re: Abortion &amp; Contraception"</a>
