Fred's list of requirements for a new pastor seem to be<br>
a very good afternoon joke! But boy, the list is so deep<br>
that we can easily see ourselves in it, rejecting what<br>
God would rather give us!<br>
.....may be we are "these people who want to hear things<br>
they like..."<br>
Have a good day everyone<br>
Ben<br>
