<title>Aug1_1994: Re:  1844 Error? Not in my Bible!</title>
<h1>Re:  1844 Error? Not in my Bible!</h1>
Benjamin Siyowi Mapani (<i>lole@ariel.ucs.unimelb.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 11 Aug 1994 14:31:17 +1000</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#246">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#246">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#246">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#246">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0247.html">Benjamin Siyowi Mapani: "Re:  SDA Reform &amp; fetters in SDA?"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0245.html">Tony Dyson: "RE: First Jerusalem SDA Church"</a>
<li> <b>Maybe in reply to:</b> <a href="0219.html">Bill Sands Jr.: "1844 Error? Not in my Bible!"</a>
