<title>Aug1_1994: Seventh Day Adventists / Eternal hell</title>
<h1>Seventh Day Adventists / Eternal hell</h1>
Peter Kooiman (<i>pko@PARADIGM.CO.ZA</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 10 Aug 1994 12:08:10 RSA-2</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#264">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#264">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#264">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#264">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0265.html">Joseph Miceli: "(no subject)"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0263.html">Clarence L. Thomas IV: "Seventh Day Adventists / Eternal hell"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
