<!-- body="start" -->
Dear all<br>
<p>
I also have concern for the people who will suffer for ever. To mention,<br>
however, that God is LOVE (which is very true) is to refer to only one<br>
characteristic. He is also just, holy, etc.  When He said that the<br>
punishment of sin is death, He meant it, love or no love, since His<br>
righteousness demands it and He really does not have another option. And He<br>
does not really care for your opinion on that score either, viz Rom 9 : 15<br>
vv (or there abouts).<br>
<p>
I have come to understand and appreciate our Father as an absolute Being,<br>
ie either black or white, wet or dry, warm or cold - nothing in between,<br>
like it or not.<br>
<p>
In Christ<br>
<p>
PETER KOOIMAN                 | Fax   : ++27-12-342-1754<br>
Paradigm Systems Technology   |<br>
Pretoria, South Africa        | DNS   : pko@paradigm.co.za<br>
