<!-- body="start" -->
         "From the SDAs On-line CompuServe Forum"        <br>
           (Call [800] 260-7171 to learn how to join)    <br>
<p>
eff:  If you have access to a fax, dial 1-800-474-4SDA and you will be connected<br>
to an automated fax service from the North American Division Supply Center.  It<br>
is free, and you can request papers on several topics such as How are<br>
Ingathering funds used?, How are tithe funds used?  What are Adventists doing<br>
about the AIDS epidemic?  After you are connected, just follow the instructions.<br>
If you request document #002, you will reveive a free listing of available<br>
topics.  You will have your response via fax in minutes.<br>
<p>
Bill <br>
