<p>
Is this the "Reformed Seventh-day Adventist Church"?  (I have a posting<br>
in the SDAnet pipeline regarding my understanding of their origins).<br>
Or does the group you refer to go by another name?<br>
<p>
I have SDA friends in California who visited a Reformed SDA church (in the<br>
higher lands east of Loma Linda).  They were welcomed politely and were<br>
permitted to join communion (which was happening that day).  A not-SDA-of-<br>
any-kind Christian visitor was there and but was not permitted to participate.<br>
My friends later showed a couple they met at that church an SoP quote wherein<br>
a non-SDA Bible-believing Christian was invited to join in foot washing/Lord's<br>
supper communion by EGW.  The Reformed SDA couple were surprised.<br>
