<title>Aug1_1994: Re: Is abortion sin?</title>
<h1>Re: Is abortion sin?</h1>
SEREM VINCENT (<i>SEREM@agreng.lan.mcgill.ca</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 10 Aug 1994 22:53:35 EST5EDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#235">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#235">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#235">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#235">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0236.html">SEREM VINCENT: "Taboo topics"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0234.html">Bill Sands Jr.: "1844  (*^&amp;$%^$&amp;$^)"</a>
