<P>
<FONT SIZE=4>Understanding its relevance and need for further
exposure, Americans for Tax Reform presents <I>I &amp; R Across
America</I>, a chart of information about the initiative and referendum
campaigns currently underway in the states.  With this chart,
you will know the state, the subject of the legislation, how many
valid signatures are required to qualify for the ballot, the deadline
for getting the initiative on the ballot and whether the initiative
is to amend the state constitution (Constitutional Amendment in
bold), to make a new law (Statute in italics), or a referred measure
by the state legislature (Referendum in plain text).   <BR>
<BR>
</FONT>
