<a href="/empower/new/reality.htm">Reality Check</a> | <a href="/empower/i-pr.html">Press Releases</a
> | <a href="/empower/speechs.html">Speeches and Lectures</a> | <a href="/empower/mission.html">What
is EA?</a> | <a href="/empower/bio.html">Biographies</a> | <a href="/empower/issue.html">Issues</a> |
 <a href="/empower/video.html">Flat Tax Ad</a> | <a href="/empower/audio.html">Audio</a> | <a href="/
empower/i-ct.html">Congressional Testimony</a> ]
<p><br>
| <A HREF="/townhall/">
Town Hall</a> |</center>
</blockquote>

<p><br>
