<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/ff/retro/future.html 204.71.237.87 19970209060558 text/html 26299
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 06:06:40 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 17-Jan-97 19:21:03 GMT
