to the taxpayers of the _____ District of the State of _______,
and to the American people that I will<BR>
<BR>
     ONE, Oppose any and all efforts to increase the marginal
income tax rates for individuals and/or businesses; and<BR>
<BR>
     TWO, Oppose any further reduction or elimination of deductions
and credits, unless matched dollar for dollar by further reducing
tax rates.<BR>
