<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Working Agenda -- CPAC</TITLE>
<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z Beta">
</HEAD>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<basefont size="2">
<center>
<a href="logo.map">
<img src="/cpac/logo-ag.gif" alt="CPAC '96" border="0" ISMAP></a>
<P>
<H2>AGENDA</H2>
</center>
<P>
<br>
<a name="top"></a>
<P>
<hr width="35%" size="3"><P>
 (All Sessions, except Press Conference, in Regency Ballroom)
<P>
<a name="thurs"></a>
<center>
<H3>THURSDAY, FEBRUARY 22, 1996</H3>
<b><a href="/cpac/fr-quest-t.html">Submit Questions for Thursday's Panels</a></b><p>
<font size="-1">
<a href="#fri">Friday</a> | <a href="#sat">Saturday</a>
</font>
</center>
<P><UL>
(Exhibit Hall Open, 12:00 - 6:00 in the Ambassador Room)
</UL><P>
<FONT SIZE=2>11:00 a.m. PRESS CONFERENCE </FONT>
<P><UL>
<FONT SIZE=2><a href="/cpac/bios.html#keene">David A. Keene</a></FONT> <FONT SIZE=2>American Conservative Union</FONT><br>
<P></UL>
<FONT SIZE=2>12:00 p.m. OPENING REMARKS</FONT>
<P><UL>
<FONT SIZE=2>David A. Keene</FONT> 
<P></UL>
<FONT SIZE=2>12:15 p.m.  <B>Hollywood's War on America</B></FONT>
<P><UL>
<FONT SIZE=2><a href="/cpac/bios.html#bennett">The Honorable Bill Bennett</a></FONT>
<br><FONT SIZE=2>INTRODUCTION:  <a href="/cpac/bios.html#bauer">Gary Bauer</a></FONT>
<P></UL>
<FONT SIZE=2>12:50 p.m <B>How to Defeat Clinton in
1996</B></FONT>
<P><UL>
<FONT SIZE=2>CHAIRMAN:  <a href="/cpac/bios.html#fahrenkopf">Frank Fahrenkopf</a></FONT><br>
<FONT SIZE=2>PANELISTS:   <a href="/cpac/bios.html#devine">Don Devine</a>, <a href="/cpac/bios.html#barnes">Fred Barnes</a>, <a href="/cpac/bios.html#mclaughlin">Jimmy McLaughlin</a>,
<a href="/cpac/bios.html#edmonds">Tom Edmonds</a></FONT>
<P></UL>
<FONT SIZE=2> 1:50 p.m. <B>Restoring American Citizenship</B></FONT>
<P><UL>
<FONT SIZE=2><a href="/cpac/bios.html#coats">U.S. Senator Dan Coats</a></FONT><br>
<FONT SIZE=2>INTRODUCTION:  <a href="/cpac/bios.html#meyerson">Adam Meyerson</a></FONT>
<P></UL>
<FONT SIZE=2> 2:15 p.m.  <B><a href="/cpac/bios.html#gramm">U.S. Senator Phil Gramm</a></B></FONT>
<P><UL>
INTRODUCTION: <a href="/cpac/bios.html#hallow">Ralph Hallow</a><P></UL>
2:55 p.m. <b>Whither Whitewater</b>
<ul><P>
<a href="/cpac/bios.html#irvine">Reed Irvine</a>, <a href="/cpac/bios.html#lindberg">Tod Lindberg</a>, <a href="/cpac/bios.html#ruddy">Christopher Ruddy</a>
</ul>
<P>
