<head>
<title>Columnists Index -- ACU</title>
</head>
<body>
<center>
<h2>ACU Columnists</h2>
</center>
<hr>
<p>
<ul>
<img align="left" alt="Photo of Donald Devine" hspace=8 vspace=20 src="columnists/devine.jpg">

<a href="columnists/devine.html"><b>Dr. Donald J. Devine</b></a>
<br>
<ul>
<li><font size=+1><a href="/conservative/columnists/dev011797.html">Will Election Shock Alter GOP's Course</a></font></center>
