<DOCNO>WT20-B15-477</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA087-000629-B044-6</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/bradley/gpurp.html 204.71.237.87 19970209062609 text/html 3824
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
